            "title": "Late-Pleistocene Phylogeography and Demographic History of Two Evolutionary Lineages of Artibeus jamaicensis (Chiroptera: Phyllostomidae) in Mexico",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Enrico A.",
                    "lastName": "Ruiz"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
