            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Roost Occupancy, Roost Site Selection and Diet of Straw-Coloured Fruit Bats (Pteropodidae: Eidolon helvum) in Western Kenya: The Need for Continued Public Education",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
