            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Seasonal and Nightly Activity Patterns of Migrating Silver-Haired Bats (Lasionycteris noctivagans) Compared to Non-Migrating Big Brown Bats (Eptesicus fuscus) at a Fall Migration Stopover Site",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
